and hang out while I pack Carson's things.

261
00:13:39,527 --> 00:13:43,364
Hey. This is Yoon Jong-shin's
limited edition record.

262
00:13:43,989 --> 00:13:45,074
My gosh.

263
00:13:45,157 --> 00:13:48,244
I searched all over
Dongmyo Flea Market but couldn't find it.

264
00:13:48,327 --> 00:13:52,706
Goodbye, my old love

265
00:13:52,790 --> 00:13:56,126
I'm preparing all day to say goodbye

266
00:13:56,210 --> 00:13:58,754
Let's go to the other side now.

267
00:13:58,921 --> 00:14:01,799
Our safari reservation is coming up,
so let's head there.

268
00:14:01,882 --> 00:14:03,092
-Are you hungry?
-No.

269
00:14:03,676 --> 00:14:05,594
I need to use the bathroom.

270
00:14:05,678 --> 00:14:06,554
Okay.

271
00:14:11,225 --> 00:14:13,310
He has never been
to an amusement park before?

272
