Liar.

273
00:14:20,025 --> 00:14:22,111
How much of it is a lie?

274
00:14:22,194 --> 00:14:23,487
Is anything true?

275
00:14:24,488 --> 00:14:26,240
What does he take me for?

276
00:14:26,740 --> 00:14:29,159
I made him work multiple jobs
and ripped him off.

277
00:14:29,702 --> 00:14:33,122
